{"article_id":"DEvTsNCDjrXECTYI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"ALEXANDRIA , Va.","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"The jury in the bank and tax fraud trial of former Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort ended its third day of deliberations on Monday","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"without reaching a verdict .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The judge said","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the jury would reconvene on Tuesday morning .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The case is the first","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to go to trial","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"stemming from Special Counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation into Russia ' s role in the 2016 U.S. presidential election ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"although the charges largely predate Manafort ' s five months","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"working on Donald Trump ' s successful campaign .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Manafort faces five counts of filing false tax returns , four counts of failing to disclose offshore bank accounts , and nine counts of bank fraud .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"If convicted on all the charges ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"he could spend the rest of his life in prison .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"A conviction would undermine efforts by Trump and some Republican lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to paint Mueller ' s Russia inquiry as a political witch hunt ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"while an acquittal would be a setback for the special counsel .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"In a break with convention , Trump weighed in on the trial on Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"calling the case against Manafort at the federal court in Alexandria , Virginia , \" very sad \"","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"and lauding his former associate as a \" very good person . \"","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"On Monday , Trump accused Mueller ' s team of \" enjoying ruining people ' s lives \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and trying to influence the elections in November","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"when Republicans will try to hold on to control of Congress .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" Mueller ' s Angry Dems are looking to impact the election .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"They are a National Disgrace ! \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Trump wrote on Twitter .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Trump ' s tweet was in reference to a New York Times report","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that White House Counsel Don McGahn had cooperated extensively with Mueller .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Before dismissing them on Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Judge T.S . Ellis reminded the jurors ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"who are not sequestered ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to refrain from discussing the case or investigating it on their own during the weekend .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Defense attorneys Kevin Downing","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"( R ) ,","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"Thomas Zehnle","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"( 2nd R )","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and Richard Westling","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"( L )","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"walk at the end of the third day of jury deliberations in the trial against Paul Manafort , President Trump 's former campaign chairman","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"who is facing bank and tax fraud charges ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"in Alexandria , Virginia , U.S. , August 20 , 2018 .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"/Joshua Roberts","depth":3},{"id":42,"text":"Some legal experts expressed concern , however ,","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"that jurors might still see Trump ' s comments","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"- inadvertently or otherwise .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Another headline from Friday","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that could grab the attention of jurors","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"concerned Ellis ' disclosure","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that he had received threats","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"related to the trial","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"and was being protected by U.S. marshals .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"The jury was not present","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"when he made those remarks .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"\" In a high profile case , the general assumption is that some outside information may accidentally reach a jury ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"despite jurors ' best efforts","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"to avoid relevant news , \"","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"said jury consultant Roy Futterman .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" Given the judge ' s statement ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"the jurors may reasonably assume","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that they may be at some risk ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"which may change the tenor of their deliberations ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"perhaps raising tensions","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"or speeding things up . \"","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"On Thursday , the jury asked for a definition of \" reasonable doubt \" and clarification on the law","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"governing the reporting of foreign bank accounts ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"but it did not ask any similar questions on Friday or Monday .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"Shanlon Wu ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"who represented Manafort ' s former protege Rick Gates","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"before he pleaded guilty in February","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and cooperated with the prosecution ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"the lack of questions might bode better for the prosecution than the defense .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"it suggested","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" they were working hard","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"and working well together ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and there was no dissension . \"","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that ' s a good sign for the prosecution , \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Wu said .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Still ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"he saw a chance of acquittals on the four counts","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"of failing to disclose foreign bank accounts ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"citing the jury ' s technical question on Thursday about the ownership and control threshold requirements for such disclosures .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":169,"left":116,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":86,"right":115,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":86,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":100,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":89,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":87,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":93,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":90,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":8,"right":91,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":11,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":94,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":16,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":102,"right":113,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":17,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":109,"right":1